{"tid":18271,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想養貓,問下關於窗網嘅野","createTime":"2016-12-02T07:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T09:01:04.000Z","uid":47314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af463ec9e86aba1d2515fa148398824abbfac3e0","tid":18271,"uid":47314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"是咪一定要裝窗網? <br />\n個窗網有冇話要點嘅樣?<br />\n全屋都要(廚房厠所)?  <br />\n全屋裝曬大概要幾錢?<br />\n同埋搵咩人裝?定要自己裝?"},{"pid":"ed8c0903e61d151314e08dd4271b257303aaa516","tid":18271,"uid":39717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咪一定要裝窗網? <br />\n個窗網有冇話要點嘅樣?<br />\n全屋都要(廚房厠所)?  <br />\n全屋裝曬大概要幾錢?<br />\n同埋搵咩人裝?定要自己裝?</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n格仔網加膠帶夠方便<br />\n要開嘅窗就要裝<br />\n睇你要裝幾多<br />\n自己裝都可以<br />\n<br />\n另，識淘寶就度好size 自己淘落黎裝<br />\n唔識就去十蚊店逐塊買返黎砌"},{"pid":"ae4801b1ce9d1f57358ba1e2b584ff36a720ea15","tid":18271,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"我都想養<br />\n耐何屋企人唔鍾意裝貓網<br />\n本身冇裝窗花<br />\n裝左格仔網幾影響外觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9d2be7daa006d993945068866813847a2cdd4d","tid":18271,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想養<br />\n耐何屋企人唔鍾意裝貓網<br />\n本身冇裝窗花<br />\n裝左格仔網幾影響外觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n整蚊網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n格仔網真係整到鐵窗邊緣咁 好樣衰"},{"pid":"f28da402eb20c80bb23442ec050a0eee62b0e0de","tid":18271,"uid":47314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>是咪一定要裝窗網? <br />\n個窗網有冇話要點嘅樣?<br />\n全屋都要(廚房厠所)?  <br />\n全屋裝曬大概要幾錢?<br />\n同埋搵咩人裝?定要自己裝?</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n格仔網加膠帶夠方便<br />\n要開嘅窗就要裝<br />\n睇你要裝幾多<br />\n自己裝都可以<br />\n<br />\n另，識淘寶就度好size 自己淘落黎裝<br />\n唔識就去十蚊店逐塊買返黎砌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n格仔網加膠帶姐係點? 有無相可以參考下?<br />\n同埋點方便法? 方便拆? 裝左都開到窗? <br />\n同埋裝左屋企會唔會好柒?"},{"pid":"d3a3c2aa94ed93096745138450df06f44497a1a4","tid":18271,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"屋企裝類似咁既樣既金屬蚊裝，仲有個lock可以固定唔驚主人整郁佢，裝左兩隻一千都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/162243_bb5477dfdd0ad420ed941f12e768a6ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F162243_bb5477dfdd0ad420ed941f12e768a6ec.jpg&h=4f42ee0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c8258c338d344085c70af6eb551e44c2622f958","tid":18271,"uid":47314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都想養<br />\n耐何屋企人唔鍾意裝貓網<br />\n本身冇裝窗花<br />\n裝左格仔網幾影響外觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n整蚊網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n格仔網真係整到鐵窗邊緣咁 好樣衰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蚊網會唔會貴啲?"},{"pid":"132ba05a81b7d863f3da93a0d7734bf783f1a2ae","tid":18271,"uid":47314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企裝類似咁既樣既金屬蚊裝，仲有個lock可以固定唔驚主人整郁佢，裝左兩隻一千都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/02/162243_bb5477dfdd0ad420ed941f12e768a6ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F02%2F162243_bb5477dfdd0ad420ed941f12e768a6ec.jpg&h=4f42ee0e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己買泥裝? 定搵人裝?"},{"pid":"013884998166cc7ed5cd11c58f65a2c38bebf815","tid":18271,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屋企裝類似咁既樣既金屬蚊裝，仲有個lock可以固定唔驚主人整郁佢，裝左兩隻一千都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hk